meta {
  name: 3 - Cross invalidation instructor
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

patch {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/instructors/{{instructorUuid}}
  body: json
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json
  Accept: application/ld+json
}

body:json {
  {
    "first_name": "Cross invalidation test"
  }
}

docs {
  Exercise 3 test — cross invalidation:
  1. GET /courses 2 times → verify the HIT
  2. Run this request (PATCH an instructor, not a course)
  3. GET /courses → HIT or MISS?

  Answer: MISS, because the Cache-Tags of /courses contain
  the IRIs of embedded instructors.
}
